HEADWORD: Semisextile
<hw>Sem"i*sex"tile</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Astrol.)</fld>
<def>An aspect of the planets when they are distant from each other the
twelfth part of a circle, or thirty degrees.</def>
<rj><au>Hutton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

